ji\" /> <br />\ndeep web同暗網都未識分....."},{"pid":"0644b53ce631371516cf744d811e54c7eb6ff2e4","tid":439784,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇住成班小朋友傾真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndeep web同暗網都未識分.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉, 其實我都未聽過暗網呢個term喎, 深網就聽過! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n深網，為深層網絡（英語：Deep Web）的略稱，又稱：不可見網、隱藏網，是指萬維網上那些不能被標準搜尋引擎索引的非表面網絡內容。深網包括許多非常常見的用途，如網絡郵件和網絡銀行等等。(Source: Wikipedia)"},{"pid":"fd07d730b1a391db1407424fbe747e00337b7877","tid":439784,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇住成班小朋友傾真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndeep web同暗網都未識分.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉, 其實我都未聽過暗網呢個term喎, 深網就聽過! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n深網，為深層網絡（英語：Deep Web）的略稱，又稱：不可見網、隱藏網，是指萬維網上那些不能被標準搜尋引擎索引的非表面網絡內容。深網包括許多非常常見的用途，如網絡郵件和網絡銀行等等。(Source: Wikipedia)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠一下, 原來真係有暗網呢樣嘢, 不過係深網其中一部分嚟! <br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9A%97%E7%BD%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259A%2597%25E7%25BD%2591&d=bdQJtR5Xuplh%2BIUX7YPb1QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=fb526dcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9A%97%E7%BD%91</a>"},{"pid":"e99d93cfdbb9b0613a52a6040c61920a2358035d","tid":439784,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:58:17.000Z","msg":"其實呢自己屋企部機set個ligin required 既server連去noip<br />\n妳都係暗網holder<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de61b2d9f1d366f6dc1b7115f05d8948e478df92","tid":439784,"uid":79442,"lik